---
title: "Kontakt - GoldClean"
description: "Kontaktieren Sie GoldClean - Wir freuen uns auf Ihre Anfrage für professionelle Reinigungsdienstleistungen."
---
<section class="hero-section min-h-[400px] md:min-h-[500px]"
          style="background-image: url(&quot;/images/technische-reinigung.webp&quot;);">
          <div class="hero-overlay"></div>
          <div class="container-custom relative z-10 text-white py-16">
            <div class="max-w-3xl">
              <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold mb-4 leading-tight">Was können wir für Sie tun?</h1>
              <p class="text-lg md:text-xl opacity-90 mb-8 max-w-2xl">Bei Fragen oder sonstigen Anliegen sind wir gerne
                für Sie da. Sie können uns jederzeit anrufen, eine Mail schreiben oder per Kontaktformular kontaktieren.
                In einem persönlichen Termin finden wir gemeinsam eine passende Lösung für Ihre Anforderungen und
                Bedürfnisse.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>
        <section class="section-padding">
          <div class="container-custom">
            <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-3 gap-12">
              <div class="space-y-8">
                <div class="hidden"></div>
                <div>
                  <h4 class="font-semibold text-primary mb-2 flex items-center gap-2"><svg
                      xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"
                      stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"
                      class="lucide lucide-phone h-5 w-5">
                      <path
                        d="M22 16.92v3a2 2 0 0 1-2.18 2 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-8.63-3.07 19.5 19.5 0 0 1-6-6 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-3.07-8.67A2 2 0 0 1 4.11 2h3a2 2 0 0 1 2 1.72 12.84 12.84 0 0 0 .7 2.81 2 2 0 0 1-.45 2.11L8.09 9.91a16 16 0 0 0 6 6l1.27-1.27a2 2 0 0 1 2.11-.45 12.84 12.84 0 0 0 2.81.7A2 2 0 0 1 22 16.92z">
                      </path>
                    </svg>Telefon</h4><a href="tel:+912345678"
                    class="text-muted-foreground hover:text-primary transition-colors">+912345678</a>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <h4 class="font-semibold text-primary mb-2 flex items-center gap-2"><svg
                      xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"
                      stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"
                      class="lucide lucide-mail h-5 w-5">
                      <rect width="20" height="16" x="2" y="4" rx="2"></rect>
                      <path d="m22 7-8.97 5.7a1.94 1.94 0 0 1-2.06 0L2 7"></path>
                    </svg>E-Mail</h4><a href="mailto:info@goldclean.de"
                    class="text-muted-foreground hover:text-primary transition-colors">info@goldclean.de</a>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <h4 class="font-semibold text-primary mb-2 flex items-center gap-2"><svg
                      xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"
                      stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"
                      class="lucide lucide-clock h-5 w-5">
                      <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle>
                      <polyline points="12 6 12 12 16 14"></polyline>
                    </svg>Bürozeiten</h4>
                  <div class="text-sm text-muted-foreground space-y-1">
                    <div class="flex justify-between max-w-xs"><span>Montag</span><span>8:00 – 17:00 Uhr</span></div>
                    <div class="flex justify-between max-w-xs"><span>Dienstag</span><span>8:00 – 17:00 Uhr</span></div>
                    <div class="flex justify-between max-w-xs"><span>Mittwoch</span><span>8:00 – 17:00 Uhr</span></div>
                    <div class="flex justify-between max-w-xs"><span>Donnerstag</span><span>8:00 – 17:00 Uhr</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex justify-between max-w-xs"><span>Freitag</span><span>8:00 – 15:00 Uhr</span></div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="lg:col-span-2">
                <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Wir freuen uns auf Ihre Anfrage</h2>
                <form class="space-y-6">
                  <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
                    <div><input type="text" placeholder="Ihr Name *" required=""
                        class="w-full px-4 py-3 border border-gray-300 rounded focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary focus:border-transparent"
                        value=""></div>
                    <div><input type="email" placeholder="Ihre E-Mail-Adresse *" required=""
                        class="w-full px-4 py-3 border border-gray-300 rounded focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary focus:border-transparent"
                        value=""></div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
                    <div><input type="tel" placeholder="Ihre Telefonnummer"
                        class="w-full px-4 py-3 border border-gray-300 rounded focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary focus:border-transparent"
                        value=""></div>
                    <div><select
                        class="w-full px-4 py-3 border border-gray-300 rounded focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary focus:border-transparent">
                        <option value="">– Bitte auswählen –</option>
                        <option value="technische">Technische Reinigung</option>
                        <option value="unterhalts">Unterhaltsreinigung</option>
                        <option value="beratung">Beraten Sie mich</option>
                      </select></div>
                  </div>
                  <div><textarea placeholder="Ihre Nachricht" rows="6"
                      class="w-full px-4 py-3 border border-gray-300 rounded focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary focus:border-transparent resize-none"></textarea>
                  </div>
                  <p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground">* Pflichtfelder<br>Sämtliche Daten werden gemäß
                    Datenschutzerklärung nur streng zweckgebunden zur Bearbeitung und Beantwortung Ihrer Anfrage
                    benutzt.</p>
                  <div class="flex items-start gap-3"><input type="checkbox" id="privacy" required=""
                      class="mt-1"><label for="privacy" class="text-sm text-muted-foreground">Ich habe die
                      Datenschutzerklärung zur Kenntnis genommen und bin damit einverstanden, dass die von mir
                      angegebenen Daten elektronisch erhoben und gespeichert werden. *</label></div><button
                    type="submit" class="btn-primary">Nachricht senden</button>
                </form>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>
        <section class="h-96 bg-secondary/50 flex items-center justify-center">
          <div class="text-center"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"
              class="lucide lucide-map-pin h-12 w-12 text-primary mx-auto mb-4">
